data.description:
**HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT ON THIS HERNANDO BEAUTY WITH AN IN-GROUND SWIMMING POOL**
This 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home in the heart of beautiful Hernando is only in need of one thing... you!  You're sure to be impressed with the hardwood flooring, split bedroom floor plan (3 beds down, 1 up plus a huge bonus!) updated kitchen with expansive storage space, neutral/updated paint throughout, large primary suite with attached spa bath, walk in attic with expandable space, oversized garage, and the amazing backyard with inground pool and privacy fencing. 
This amazing home is completely move-in ready and located in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in DeSoto County, so don't delay! Call your favorite agent TODAY to see 2363 St. Ives. You'll be glad you did!
